ures), as well as recommending what to do to make your app more secure (sometimes even decently secure).</p><p></p><p>Have you had this problem as well? If yes, how do you tackle it?</p><p></p>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "3608689", "name": "Constantine", "username": "aeromaniax", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/3608689/4d219708-cb00-47fd-b85e-7f989b9720f1.jpeg", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": false, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": null, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 14, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 8, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "472520", "slug": "vibecoding", "subject": {"id": "201", "name": "Vibecoding", "thumbnailUuid": "379b8fc1-a8e0-48f3-be0c-15e11b165944.svg", "__typename": "DiscussionCategory"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "753695", "pageViewsCount": 145, "slug": "introducing-fakeradar-real-time-deepfake-detection-for-video-calls", "createdAt": "2025-09-23T02:04:38-07:00", "path": "/p/self-promotion/introducing-fakeradar-real-time-deepfake-detection-for-video-calls", "title": "Introducing FakeRadar: Real-Time Deepfake Detection for Video Calls", "descriptionPreview": "<p>Hi Product Hunters!</p><p>I m Artem Anikeev, founder of FakeRadar.io the world's first real-time deepfake detection tool designed specifically for video calls.</p><p>Why FakeRadar?</p><p>The rise of deepfake technology has brought new risks to everyday digital communication. From fraudulent job interviews to high-stake banking scams, the threat is real - and constantly evolving. FakeRadar was born to address this urgent need with cutting-edge, accessible technology.</p>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "8850151", "name": "Artem Anikeev", "username": "artem_anikeev", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/8850151/a06e9719-